{"tid":1185030,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇手足機場黎","createTime":"2019-06-04T04:23:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T07:13:47.000Z","uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"24043bbed3a4036b46a3031447ee1c8968cfe190","tid":1185030,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T04:23:15.000Z","msg":"沉寂一時的巴士「刺客」疑再重現！今日(4日)早上接近9時，一輛開往機場的S64X龍運巴士，在駛至東涌逸東邨巴士站時，上層一名坐於靠近車尾第五排的姓文(30歲)女乘客向車長表示，左腳遭前座椅背一支針筒拮傷，車長於是停車報警。救護車到場，將女事主送院治理。警員調查後，發現肇事的針筒並無外殼，並且經前座座位插穿椅背，再拮傷女事主，案件現交由大嶼山警區重案組接手調查。"},{"pid":"8560c139d52464c5270f6d2f4fa099f39d67cc06","tid":1185030,"uid":38189,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T04:23:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b0f48d4f5c783820ed7e9ec52555cf68db1220","tid":1185030,"uid":9004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8560c139d52464c5270f6d2f4fa099f39d67cc06","tid":1185030,"uid":38189,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T04:23:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T04:24:41.000Z","msg":"玩到入機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94673064095d9617ee697ddd0dc354cc9ecd0943","tid":1185030,"uid":66357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T04:26:16.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"af66a74e86da81bd339a24b64406d1e1dd6861cf","tid":1185030,"uid":17606,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T04:27:38.000Z","msg":"over左啦牙賓"},{"pid":"42fc2a519a22eb9f43e7742a88352fd26b90befd","tid":1185030,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af66a74e86da81bd339a24b64406d1e1dd6861cf","tid":1185030,"uid":17606,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T04:27:38.000Z","msg":"over左啦牙賓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T04:31:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hk